                <h1 id="homeHeading">A simple Tool for an increasingly complex world.</h1>
                <hr>
                <p class="text-faded">The bandwidth of any team to handle increased operational complexity is finite. For every new, advanced solution that is added, this operational bandwidth shrinks.
                  BUT, if we can implement methods to make these solutions easier to consume, we can free up some of that bandwidth to allow us to do more. That's where Eucalyptus comes in.</p>
