    <section class="bg-primary" id="about">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2 text-center">
                    <h2 class="section-heading">Solving Complexity with Simplicity</h2>
                    <hr class="light">
                    <p class="text-faded">Eucalyptus leverages <b>Flight Plans</b> to provide teams with easy, step-by-step guidance to manage systems. Every time a <b>Pilot</b> takes off, they can leverage <b>Flight Plans</b> to guide, track, and document their <b>Flights</b>.<br><br>
                      <b>Flights</b> utilizing <b>FlightPlans</b> can be saved, loaded, and stored to allow picking up where you left off, or simply checking back later to confirm what how the <b>flight</b> was navigated. When completing a <b>flight</b>, notes are saved per each step and sub-step to allow tracking progress.</p>
                    <a href="#features" class="page-scroll btn btn-splash-default btn-splash-xl sr-button">Explore Features!</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

